'''Bargainer''' was a title for the leader of a [[Qom Jha and Qom Qae|Qom Jha]] nesting. The title was also used by the [[Qom Jha and Qom Qae|Qom Qae]] who gave the title to the eldest member of the nesting. [[Eater Of Fire Creepers]] was a Bargainer for his nesting.

